commit 2aaa5ceeefc1754299e1bf98b40f091683d162bf
Author: Jiri Kraus <jkraus@nvidia.com>
Date:   Tue Oct 15 10:01:05 2024 +0200

    Added User Buffer Registration option to NCCL variants.
---
 README.md               |  3 +++
 nccl/jacobi.cpp         | 45 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++----
 nccl_graphs/jacobi.cpp  | 44 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++----
 nccl_overlap/jacobi.cpp | 45 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++----
