    nvshmem_opt: Add custom barrier for jacobi

    This commit adds a custom barrier for the jacobi app.
    The jacobi app in this repo does not need a global
    barrier. Rather, each rank just needs to synchronize
    with its neighbor before moving on to the next iteration.
    This custom barrier does exaclty that and hence will
    be faster than using shmem_barrier_all, especially
    when we strong scale to large PE count.
